snippet.title: Cats on Duty — PC Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Cats on Duty is a purr-fect blend of tower defense and match-3 mechanics. Manage two game fields at once, arm and upgrade your cat towers to defeat hordes of enemies and show the armies of undead who's the biggest cat in town!

OUT MEOW ON #Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2447260/Cats_on_Duty/
AND ON #EpicGamesStore: https://store.epicgames.com/p/cats-on-duty-87b2ae
